parameters:
\nc<>Ding dong, it's the mail. I'll leave it in front of the
door.
\nc<>Someone sent mail. The sender's information is not written.

\nc<>When I opened the box, there was a piece of cloth that
persistently showed only the important parts, and a belt
tied with used condoms, along with a letter.

\nc<>A gift for the perverts who fill the apartment with moans
every night.
\nc<>They have such a terrible taste in gifts.

\nc<>I put it in the closet for now, as it might be evidence to
catch the criminal.

\nc<>From the top left, you can check what week it is and what
day of the week it is.

\nc<>In the game, there is a concept called turn, and a day is
composed of two turns. Additionally, a day is composed of
daytime and nighttime.
\nc<>Kei can freely act twice a day.

\nc<>Every Friday, villains will invade.
On the day of the
invasion, we must go and stop the villains, and it will
consume one day.
\nc<>You can transform into Levantia from this magic circle.

\nc<>The reactions and events of NPCs are different depending on
whether it's Kei's form or Levantia's form.

\nc<>You can go to the hideout of magical girls Candy & Sherbet
from here.

\nc<>You can now freely go back and forth between the hideout and
the flashback room.

\nc<>The map is divided into five regions, and Kei chooses one
region to go out.

\nc<>Each event placed in each region consumes one turn, and if
you complete all the events, you will return home.

\nc<>In the game, there are true endings, normal endings, and
four types of bad endings prepared.

\nc<>If you find the gameplay difficult, you can check hints for
the story from the item -> precious memories.

\nc<>Whether to defeat the villains and save the world, or to
corrupt Kei, it all depends on your choices.
\nc<>Well then, please look forward to it.
